OL,5, More than 30 current and former        
OL,6, Metropolitan Police officers are suing 
OL,7, the force "for personal injury and     
OL,8, losses following their role in the     
OL,9, Grenfell Tower fire", it says.         
OL,11,FThe Met told the BBC a total of 27     
OL,12,Fserving and six former officers are    
OL,13,Fpursuing civil claims over the matter. 
OL,15,FA spokesperson added the case is       
OL,16,Fcurrently stayed until December 2024,  
OL,17,Fwhen further discussions will happen.  
OL,19,FIt comes in response to an article in  
OL,20,Fthe Sunday Times about the legal claim.
